## Voice collection sidebar content

varying-pronunciations-explanation-1 = Cabaqa adda addaa ni simannaa! Kiliippii dubbisaan jecha tokko dogoggoraan dubbate, dhiphina bakka hin taane kaa’e, ykn mallattoolee addaan kutuu tuffate jettee yaaddu jettee diduu kee dura of eeggannoo guddaa godhi. Addunyaa irratti sagaleen adda addaa kan itti fayyadamaa jiru yoo ta’u, isaan keessaa tokko tokko hawaasa naannoo keessanii keessatti hin dhageenye ta’a. Mee warra sirraa adda taʼee dubbachuu dandaʼaniif dinqisiifannaa arjummaadhaan kenni.
varying-pronunciations-explanation-2 = Akkataa dubbii garaagaraa ni simanna! Yoo dubbistuun jecha karaa dogoggoraan dubbate, dhiphina jecha bakka dogoggoraa kaa’e, yookaan mallattoolee qubee tuffate ta’e, kilippii sana hatattamaan balleessuu dura baay’ee of eeggadhaa. Addunyaa guutuu keessatti akkaataa dubbii garaagaraa hedduun jiru; muraasni isaanii hawaasa naannoo keessan keessatti dhaga’amu danda’u. Mee namoota akkaataa keessan irraa adda ta’een dubbatanitti gara laafinaan fi kabajaan ilaalaa.
varying-pronunciations-example = Xurrichi ifa hin turre.
varying-pronunciations-tip-1 = [Ingiliffa Kaanaadaa keessatti sagaleen “route” akka “rowt” fakkaachuu danda’a]
varying-pronunciations-tip-2 = [Ingiliffa Biritish keessatti akka “root” dubbatamuu danda’a]
offensive-content-explanation = Himoonni adeemsa hawaasa-jiddugaleessa ta’een qoratamu, haa ta’u malee adeemsi kun guutuu miti. Yoo hima si mufachiisu ykn si gaddisiisu argite ykn dhageesse - fakkeenyaaf sababa inni <participationGuidelines>qajeelfama hirmaannaa hawaasaa</participationGuidelines> keenya cabsuuf - maaloo UI keessatti qartuu alaabaa fayyadami. Akkasumas <emailFragment>commonvoice@mozilla.com</emailFragment> irratti nu qunnamuu dandeessa
misreadings-explanation-1 = Jechoota fuula irratti argaman hunda sirritti dubbisuun dhimma baasa. Yeroo dhaggeeffattu wanti waraabame sirriitti waan barreeffame ta’uu isaa of eeggannoo guddaan ilaali; jechoota itti dabalaman, walitti yoo qabaman ykn yoo darban ni didda.
misreadings-explanation-2 = Irraa kaannaa barsiifatame dabalatee:
misreadings-explanation-3 = 'A' ykn 'The'tu jalqaba waraabbii irratti dagatameera.
misreadings-explanation-4 = Dhuma jechaa irratti 's'tu dagatameera.
misreadings-explanation-5 = Dubbisa jechoota gabaajeffaman qubeen kan isa hin taane, kanneen akka "We're" jedhu bakka "We are" jedhu dubbachuun, yookiin isa biraa dubbachuun.
misreadings-explanation-6 = Waraabbii sagalee saffisaan addaan kutuun, jecha dhumaa sirriitti xumuruun hin danda’amne.
misreadings-explanation-7 = Jecha tokko dubbisuuf carraa hedduu fudhachuu.
misreadings-example-1 = Buna dhuguuf bahaa jirra.
misreadings-example-2 = Buna dhuguuf bahaa jirra.
misreadings-example-3 = Buna dhuguuf bahaa jirra.
misreadings-example-4 = Bambilbiin saffisaan deeme.
misreadings-tip-1 = [“Nuhi” ta'uu qaba]
misreadings-tip-2 = [Barruu innikkaa keessa ‘a’n hin jiru]
misreadings-tip-3 = [Qabiyyee hinfiroomne]
background-noise-explanation = Jecha waraabbii sanaa hunda dhagahuu danda'uu qabda. Algoorizimoonni barumsa maashinii sagalee duubaa adda addaa akka keessummeessuu danda’an barbaanna, muuziqaan duubaa sagalee guddaa ykn callisaa ta’e illee hanga barreeffamicha guutuu akka hin dhageenye si hin dhowwineetti fudhatama qabaachuu danda’a. Haa ta'u malee, ciccitni ykn 'caccabni' sagalicha akka hin dhageenye si dhorku yoo jiraate, kilippii sana diduu qabda.
background-noise-example-1 = Daaynoosaroota gurguddoo bara Tiriyaassik
background-noise-example-2 = [Haxxifannaa] [qufaa] Triassic daaynoosaroota gurguddoo.
background-noise-example-3 = Daaynoosarii guddaa [haxxiffannaa] Tiriyaassik.
background-noise-example-4 = [Crackle] daayinoosaroota gurguddoo [crackle]-riyaassik.
background-noise-tip-1 = [wacaa dudduubaan adda kan cite]
background-noise-tip-2 = [Barruu tokko guutummaan dhagahamuu hin danda’u]
background-voices-explanation = Sagaleen dudduubaa xiqqoon homaa miti, garuu namni biraa jechoota adda ta'an yeroo dubbatu yoo dhaga'uu dandeesse kilippiin sun didamuu qaba. Akkaataa idileetti kun kan ta’u bakka TVn ibsametti, ykn bakka haasawaan naannoo sanatti deemaa jirutti.
background-voices-example-1 = Daaynoosaroota gurguddoo kan Tiriyaassik. [sagalee tokkoon dubbisi]
background-voices-tip-1 = Dhufaa jirtaa? [kan biraan waamamuu]
volume-explanation = Sagaleen dubbataa garaagaraa ni jiraata. Yoo sagaleen olka’ee waraabbiin adda ciccite ykn sagaleen gadi bu’e guutuun barruu yoo hin dhagahamne haqi.
reader-effects-explanation = Waraabbiin hedduun sagalee namaa dhugaa keessaa fudhatame. Galmee sirrii hin taane kan sagalee olka’e, xiqqoo dubbate, ykn “dramatic” ta’e ni fudhatama. Galmee sirrii hin taane kan sirbame fi sagalee computer-synthesized fayyadame haqi.
just-unsure-explanation = Yoo wanti qajeelfama kana keessatti hin kaafamne si mudate, sagalee irratti murtii keetiin vote gochuu. Yoo murtii hin dandeenye, button “Darbi” fayyadami, kiliippiitti itti fufi.
still-have-questions = Ammayyuu gaaffii olkaa'aa?
contact-common-voice = Garee Common Voice qunnami

