## Sentence collection sidebar content

public-domain-explanation-1 = Himoonni barruu hundi <publicDomain>domeenii uummataa</publicDomain> (<cc0>cc0</cc0>) ta'uun isaanii baay'ee barbaachisaa dha sababiin isaas kuusaan deetaa Sagalee Waliigalaa hayyama cc0 jalatti gadhiifama. Yoomiyyuu hima tokko yoo mirkaneeffatte qofa olkaa'i, yeroo hunda immoo caqasa barbaachisaa ta'e dabali.
public-domain-explanation-2 = Himoonni filatamoon injiinii dubbii beekamtii kennuuf faayidaa qabu ijaaruuf gargaaran, afaan haasawa guyyaa guyyaa fi jecha ammayyaa ta’uu qabu. Yaadonni hima maddisiisuuf si gargaaran keessaa muraasni:
public-domain-explanation-3 = Ofiin yookaan hiriyoota kee fi hawaasa afaan kee waliin himoota ammayyaa fi afaan haasawa guyyaa guyyaa ta’an uumi – fakkeenyaaf, sagantaa “toonii-a-barruun” geggeessuun.
public-domain-explanation-4 = Barreessitoota, qopheessitoota taphaa (playwrights) yookaan barreessitoota iskiriiptii qunnami, hojii isaanii keessaa kutaa xiqqoo gara public domainitti kunnuuf eeyyamamaa akka ta’an gaafadhu.
public-domain-explanation-5 = Barruuwwan copyright hin taane barbaadi – fakkeenyaaf, kitaabota 1920 dura maxxanfaman hedduu.
public-domain-explanation-6 = Mootummoota, dhaabbilee bu'aaf maleeyyii fi dhaabbilee miidiyaa qunnami; odeeffannoo marsariitii, gabaasaalee yookaan qabiyyee biraa isaanii gara public domainitti kennamuu danda’uu ilaali.
citing-sentences-explanation-1 = Madda barreessuu (citations) dabalachuun barbaachisaa dha, akka himoonni public domain keessa jiranii fi copyright itti hin fe’amne mirkaneeffachuu dandeenyuuf.
citing-sentences-subheader-websites = Marsariitii
citing-sentences-subheader-websites-explanation = Marsariitii kana dabaluu dandeessa, fkn "Common Voice - https://commonvoice.mozilla.org/".
citing-sentences-subheader-academic-reference = Wabeeffannoo Akkaadaamii
citing-sentences-subheader-academic-reference-explanation = Akka fakkeenyaatti, sirna madda qorannoo (academic referencing) fayyadamu dandeessa, fakkeenyaaf, Harvard style: "Mozilla (2021) Common Voice. Available at https://commonvoice.mozilla.org/ (Accessed: 15th September 2021)"
citing-sentences-subheader-offline-sources = Horata Ooflaayinii
citing-sentences-subheader-offline-sources-explanation = Barruu public domain kan marsariitii irra hin jirreef, sirna madda qorannoo (academic referencing) fayyadamuu dandeessa, fakkeenyaaf, Harvard style: "Jess (2021) My Public license poems"
