adding-sentences-subheader-speakable = Dubbatamaa (dubbatamuu kan danda'u)
adding-sentences-subheader-speakable-explanation = Himoonni gaariin uumamaa fi haasawa kan ta’an — namni tokko dubbisuuf salphaa ta’uu qabu. Heddumina sagalee fi jechoota adda addaa hima keessatti barbaachisaa ta’us, hima waraabuun hawaasa tola ooltummaa keenyaaf hanga danda’ametti akka bobba’aa fi bashannansiisaa ta’uuf yaalaa jirra.
adding-sentences-subheader-numbers = Lakkoofsota
adding-sentences-subheader-numbers-explanation = Akka yaadaatti, barruu horataa keessatti lakkoofsonni (digits) jiraachuu hin qaban, sababni isaas yeroo sagaleen dubbifamu rakkoo uumu danda’u. Akkaataa lakkoofsi itti dubbifamu haala irratti hundaa’a; kunis daataa-seetii keessatti burjaajii fiduu danda’a. Fakkeenyaaf, lakkoofsi “2409” sirnaan “digdamii afur duwwaa sagal” yookaan “kuma lamaa fi dhibba afurii fi sagal” jedhamee dubbifamuu danda’a.
adding-sentences-subheader-abbreviations = Gabaajeewwanii fi Bakka Bu'oota
adding-sentences-subheader-abbreviations-explanation = Gabaajeewwanii fi bakka bu'oota akka “USA” yookaan “ICE” barruu horataa keessatti irraa fagaachuun gaariidha, sababni isaas akkaataa barreeffama isaanii wajjin walsimuun dubbifamuu dhiisuu danda’u. Dabalataanis, gabaajeen tokko karaa sirrii hedduun dubbifamuu danda’a.
adding-sentences-subheader-punctuation = Sirna Tuqaalee
adding-sentences-subheader-punctuation-explanation = Mallattoolee addaa fi sirna tuqaalee yeroo baay’ee barbaachisaa ta’etti qofa dabaluu qabna. Fakkeenyaaf, apostroofiin jechoota Ingilizii akka “don’t” fi “we’re” keessatti argama; kanaafuu barruu maddaa keessatti dabalamuun isaa sirriidha. Garuu mallattoolee addaa akka “@” yookaan “#” fayyadamuun yeroo baay’ee hin barbaachisu.
adding-sentences-subheader-special-characters = Arfiiwwan Addaa fi Qubeewwan Ambaa
adding-sentences-subheader-special-characters-explanation-1 = Qubeewwan afaan dubbifamaa jiru keessaa isaan sirrii ta’uu qabu. Fakkeenyaaf, qubeen “ж” kan Raashiyaa keessaa tokko dha, garuu Ingiliffa keessatti hin fayyadamnu; kanaafuu barruu horataa Ingiliffaa keessatti gonkumaa mul’achuu hin qabu.
adding-sentences-subheader-special-characters-explanation-2 = Yeroo afaan tokko hiikamu, afaanonni qajeelfama mirkaneessuu ofii isaanii dabalataa qabaachuu danda’u. Yoo afaan tokkoof faayiliin mirkaneessuu addaa hin jirre ta’e, qajeelfamoonni Ingiliffaa gumaachitootaaf ni mul’atu.
adding-sentences-subheader-offensive-content = Qabiyyee Arrabsoo
adding-sentences-subheader-offensive-content-explanation = Yoo himni sun nama mufachiisa yookaan nama aarsa<emailFragment> ta’e – fakkeenyaaf, qabiyyee ifa ta'uu hin malle yookaan jeeqa ta'e karaa <communityGuidelines>qajeelfama hirmaannaa hawaasaa</communityGuidelines> keenyaa – hima sana diduu qabda. Akkasumas dhimma kana bal'isuu yoo barbaadde, <emailFragment>commonvoice@mozilla.com</emailFragment> irratti nu qunnami.
reviewing-sentences-explanation-1 = Yoo himni sun ulaagaalee olitti ibsaman guute, qabduu “Haaya” cuqaasi.
reviewing-sentences-explanation-2 = Yoo himni sun ulaagaalee olitti ibsaman guutuu baate, qabduu “Lakki” cuqaasi.
reviewing-sentences-explanation-3 = Yoo hima sana irratti shakkii qabaatte, irra darbiitee isa itti aanuutti ce’uu dandeessa.
reviewing-sentences-explanation-4 = Gamaggamuuf himootni yoo sinjalaa dhumatan, maaloo himoota dabalataa akka walitti qabnuuf nu gargaaraa!
domain-explanation = “Domain” jechuun mata-duree hima sanaa jechuudha. Ammaaf, filannoo keessaa filachuu dandeessa:

