transcribe-the-audio-subheader-1-explanation = Walumaa gala, wanta dhageesse hunda galmee keessatti barreessuu qabda. Kunis kan hammatu;
transcribe-the-audio-subheader-1-explanation-example-1 = Dogoggora sagalee barreessuu, turtii fi irra-deddeebii  dabalata
transcribe-the-audio-subheader-1-explanation-example-2 = Taateewwan waca sagalee akka qufaa yookaan kolfaa maqaa itti gochuu
