transcribe-the-audio-subheader-2-example-2-wrong = <wrong>Dogoggora</wrong>: <underline> 2015tti </underline> sin arga
transcribe-the-audio-subheader-2-example-3-correct = <correct>Sirrii</correct>: Dhibbeentaa digdama hir’ateera
transcribe-the-audio-subheader-2-example-3-wrong = <wrong>Dogoggora</wrong>: 20% hir’ateera
transcribe-the-audio-subheader-2-example-4-correct = <correct>Sirrii</sirrii>: Kamisa darbe <underline>FBI</underline>n to'annoo jala oolaniiru
